A vintage-style technical illustration showing an intricate maze of interconnected brass pipes, gears, and pneumatic tubes arranged in a complex flowchart pattern against aged parchment paper. The mechanical pathways branch and converge like an elaborate steampunk decision tree, with small glass chambers at junction points containing swirling colored smoke indicating different flow directions. Copper conduits twist elegantly through the composition, some paths leading to ornate Victorian gauges and dials, others disappearing into mysterious brass boxes with intricate filigree. The overall composition suggests the inner workings of a thinking machine, with pathways illuminated by warm amber gaslight glowing from within the transparent sections. Sepia tones dominate with accents of verdigris green and polished copper orange.
